INSTALL
==================

Install VIM::Packager

    $ cpan VIM::Packager


    $ vim-packager build
    $ make install

USAGE
==================
move your cursor to the subroutine declaration.

    sub my_sub {   # move to this line

    }
    
press

    <C-c><C-p>

then the pod will be filled.


we also support Template::Declare, pod will be filled like this:

    =head2 TEMPLATE xxx

    =cut

    template 'xxx' => sub { 

    };







